{"tid":1167353,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"黃手套之亂過後：香港出色嘅插畫家你又知幾個？","createTime":"2019-05-23T03:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T08:48:41.000Z","uid":242482,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d12ec715e9525a25cf9710a3cc1df430608eb672","tid":1167353,"uid":242482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:46:03.000Z","msg":"2019年，香港插畫界發生咗一件驚天地泣鬼神嘅世紀大事，真係可比最近上映嘅《復仇者聯盟4：最終之戰》，只要稍為有留意香港插畫家，都一定會知道呢單史稱「黃手套之亂」嘅傳奇。「黃手套之亂」由Cuson、草日兩位知名插畫家無意間創造出嚟，事源係Cuson係IG放咗佢同女友握手嘅放閃畫作，草日戥Cuson開心，畫咗張圖話佢筆下角色阿三都同想愛人握手，點知握到隻洗碗嘅黃手套，叫佢洗碗。星星之火可以燎原，隨住Cuson基情回應，愈演愈烈，仲有勁多本土插畫家加入戰團，成立咗「服藥者聯盟」，真係好鬼得意！亦都因為咁，令唔少人都話，哇原來香港有咁多插畫家。香港文化咁生鬼，真係好值得我哋有更多嘅關注。今日就等DailyView用網路大數據同你細數香港唔同嘅插畫家，列出最多人討論嘅二十位嘅藝術家。一齊睇睇你最鍾意邊個喇！<br />\n<br />\n10 阿塗，純種八十後高登仔<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;鵰娜猩！頂硬上！<br />\n高登神獸，金翅仆街鳥、麒麟怪、五毛蟷、小學雞，咁多耳熟能詳嘅動物畫作，全部都係出自阿塗隻手！早喺2011年，阿塗已經紅爆高登，仲組織埋關心時事嘅「鍵盤戰線」，力反網絡23條，今時今日我哋仲有得二次創作，佢哋真係出咗唔少心力。除咗神獸創作，阿塗近年往香港文化廣東話嘅題材發展，出咗《圖解廣東話》，仲喺2018年舉辦《廣東話好雙語》個人畫展，相當「貼地」，力撐本土！<br />\n<img src=\"https://dvblob.blob.core.windows.net/dvblob/Content/Upload/ThemeImages/2019-05/af9ec2e1-72b0-4e34-9cc6-29c435ba8953.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdvblob.blob.core.windows.net%2Fdvblob%2FContent%2FUpload%2FThemeImages%2F2019-05%2Faf9ec2e1-72b0-4e34-9cc6-29c435ba8953.png&h=91a8ae2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nimage source:Facebook:阿塗<br />\n<br />\n9 爵爵&amp;貓叔，JIEJIEHK<br />\n──香港同台灣嘅文化橋樑<br />\n爵爵，住喺香港嘅台灣人；貓叔，逗留過台灣嘅香港人，兩個合作插圖設計，至今已經突破咗48萬Likes。當初貓叔去台北實習半年，Fd搭Fd咁識咗對方，後嚟爵爵想出國發展，決定去香港，仲同貓叔做埋同事。亦都係呢個時期，佢哋正式開咗FB Page畫圖，幾經辛苦，終於有今日嘅成就。佢哋嘅創作以「台港文化」為主，好似飲食大不同咁，亦關心公義嘅事，最近逃犯條例都有講，真點香港人！<br />\n<img src=\"https://dvblob.blob.core.windows.net/dvblob/Content/Upload/ThemeImages/2019-05/bed53c34-bb9a-4b98-a574-764cbdd1b720.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdvblob.blob.core.windows.net%2Fdvblob%2FContent%2FUpload%2FThemeImages%2F2019-05%2Fbed53c34-bb9a-4b98-a574-764cbdd1b720.png&h=0b8bac88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nimage source:IG:jiejie_unclecat<br />\n<br />\n8 清潔龍阿德，阿德team<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;土生土長唔離地<br />\n呢幾年政府做咩都總係俾人負評，但唯獨食環署推出嘅吉祥物，唔理你黃藍紅黑統統都讚好，原因無他嘅，就係廣告公司嘅「阿德team」真係好畀心機，用嘅好潮好in好貼地嘅圖像，塑造咗清潔龍阿德出嚟。阿德宣傳公德，絕對唔係講幾句口號就算，成日都借唔同熱門時事抽水之餘，仲講埋自己嘅理念。2018年佢哋仲創作首非常爆嘅Trap music，上埋台演出，不愧為最正嘅政府吉祥物。<br />\n<img src=\"https://dvblob.blob.core.windows.net/dvblob/Content/Upload/ThemeImages/2019-05/596b3cc3-99d3-4e8b-b7df-89f59c41b467.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdvblob.blob.core.windows.net%2Fdvblob%2FContent%2FUpload%2FThemeImages%2F2019-05%2F596b3cc3-99d3-4e8b-b7df-89f59c41b467.png&h=1ba12b30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nimage source:Facebook:清潔龍阿德 Keep Clean Ambassador Ah Tak<br />\n<br />\n7 DDED，Albert&amp;Eric<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;設計呢啲，好有意思<br />\n留鬚型男Albert同Eric組成嘅設計團隊DDED，對創作相當有熱情，由廣告業轉做個人創作，最初以「偽8-bit」嘅2D平面像素仿電視遊戲畫面，制作惡搞兼諷刺動畫影片，大受網民歡迎。2014年，仲為萬寧設計「龍友大戰萬寧貓」嘅廣告，真係打入埋電視市場，連師奶都話正。2014年打後，DDED仲要由平面設計殺入立體玩具，全部設計都係有香港獨特嘅文化，好似地盤工人咁，唔買都埋嚟睇喇喂！<br />\n<img src=\"https://dvblob.blob.core.windows.net/dvblob/Content/Upload/ThemeImages/2019-05/95ad5e44-df49-4801-ace6-62e664ed29aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdvblob.blob.core.windows.net%2Fdvblob%2FContent%2FUpload%2FThemeImages%2F2019-05%2F95ad5e44-df49-4801-ace6-62e664ed29aa.png&h=2a441f41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nimage source:IG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />DED<br />\n<br />\n6 謝曬皮，TSE SAI PEI<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;努力上進嘅幸運兒 <br />\n謝曬皮，喺香港插畫界相當知名、受歡迎嘅插畫家，圖文絕不傳統，處處都可見佢獨特嘅黑色幽默同美學風格。佢畢業於香港浸會大學視覺藝術系，因為返工返到個人「謝曬皮」，人生要另尋出口，2012年喺FB開Page畫圖，好多網民做咗佢Fans。香港人有邊個唔係返工返到頹？唔怪得大家都咁鍾意佢嘅。佢話自己係幸運兒，其實佢2015年仲去英國進修，唔會固步自封，呢份努力又點止幸運咁簡單。<br />\n<img src=\"https://dvblob.blob.core.windows.net/dvblob/Content/Upload/ThemeImages/2019-05/ca9b0f5c-c888-4b24-a4dc-43a1c0ece63a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdvblob.blob.core.windows.net%2Fdvblob%2FContent%2FUpload%2FThemeImages%2F2019-05%2Fca9b0f5c-c888-4b24-a4dc-43a1c0ece63a.png&h=e1d9d222&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nimage source:Facebook:謝曬皮 TSE SAI PEI the incapable<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://dvblob.blob.core.windows.net/dvblob/Content/Upload/ThemeImages/2019-05/c17da04d-0ed9-4b2f-8e5a-13ab1c9a8722.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdvblob.blob.core.windows.net%2Fdvblob%2FContent%2FUpload%2FThemeImages%2F2019-05%2Fc17da04d-0ed9-4b2f-8e5a-13ab1c9a8722.png&h=b1a3cd30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貼到好攰，自己入去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://dailyview.tw/hk/Daily/2019/05/20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdailyview.tw%2Fhk%2FDaily%2F2019%2F05%2F20&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=becc5d6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://dailyview.tw/hk/Daily/2019/05/20</a>"},{"pid":"1f8d768beaedb681e8d207158c22f469e31b1fe7","tid":1167353,"uid":230777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:58:29.000Z","msg":"清泉：鹿零淥六四"},{"pid":"2917b17f32718675d1901844a669ea6537cbbe83","tid":1167353,"uid":119478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:01:48.000Z","msg":"1356唔識<br />\n48個名好似臭左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd80bb6d82cce09145cc407160c3465bc6db092","tid":1167353,"uid":15658,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:03:39.000Z","msg":"藍橘子明明作家點解變左插畫家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3408291ce30861526a67365a640a248b714f11ab","tid":1167353,"uid":242482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfd80bb6d82cce09145cc407160c3465bc6db092","tid":1167353,"uid":15658,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:03:39.000Z","msg":"藍橘子明明作家點解變左插畫家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:30:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n張圖同內文不符"},{"pid":"e170d84244005953898d0c9423c892e08f0efd5c","tid":1167353,"uid":14625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:36:54.000Z","msg":"張飛人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n插女家就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9276cbf090d052d24c6be7201c14cd311dadf7","tid":1167353,"uid":159342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:40:37.000Z","msg":"張飛人唔係寫故既咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好在冇「一個人」同朦豬部落」果兩個撚屌"},{"pid":"c2eb926c46520cdb70140e0dd5f5c314c79cbd3c","tid":1167353,"uid":4543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T06:44:47.000Z","msg":"冇個識，我係咪好out<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47e62dc3f25e2b2a8acbccdc9e2948f791997c4","tid":1167353,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"大大"},{"pid":"f0498bdccf2b2259ec0fa36132b307c9c69a79df","tid":1167353,"uid":120355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T08:48:41.000Z","msg":"見到黃手套就即UNLIKE"}]}